Eaagads Limited bụ ụlọ ọrụ kọfị dịkwazi na obodo  Kenya
O nwere isi ụlọ ọrụ na Obodo Nairobi na ụlọ ọrụ na Kiambu county
E debanyere aha Eaagads Limited n’afo 1946 ma depụta ya na Nairobi Securities Exchange na azụmaahịa n'okpuru akara EGAD.
Eaagads na-etinye aka na ịzụlite, ịgwakọta, na ire ngwaahịa kọfị ma n'ógbè ma n'ahịa mba ụwa niile
Ọ bụ Kofinaf Company Limited na-achịkwa ma na-achịkọta ya, ụlọ ọrụ edebanyere aha na Republik nke Kenya. Kofinaf nwere 61.74 pacenti nke isi obodo Eaagads
N'afọ 2010, ụlọ ọrụ ahụ rere ụfọdụ ala ya na obodo Tatu, ọrụ mmepe ihe onwunwe nke Renaissance Partners nke dị na obodo Moscow

Nke a dugara na ọnụahịa nke ụlọ ọrụ 63.5 pacenti  nke ndị na-etinye ego na-atụ anya nnukwu uru site na ngalaba ụlọ ọrụ na-eto eto nke Kenya. Nzukọ a bịara ná njedebe mgbe ndị isi ụlọ ọrụ ahụ mere ka o doo anya na Eaagads abụghị akụkụ nke Tatu City Project ma ga-anọgide na-arụ ọrụ dịka ụlọ ọrụ kọfị.
